facts_and_links: {'Trivia': ["Due to spending most of the budget of the film on archival fashion, the production couldn't afford renting out the Hollywood Walk of Fame to film the music video for the song of the same name, so Miley Cyrus and the production team simply filmed there very late at night, without a permit. Due to the sidewalk being incredibly dirty, Cyrus ended up with a severe knee infection that sent her to the ICU.", 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt36590404/trivia/?ref_=tt_dyk_trv'], 'Crazy credits': ['The music video for "Give Me Love" plays on the left of the end credits for their entire duration.', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt36590404/crazycredits/?tab=cz&ref_=tt_dyk_cc'], 'Soundtracks': ['PreludeWritten by Miley Cyrus, Maxx Morando, Cole Haden, Shawn Everett, Jonathan Rado, and Michael PollackProduced by Miley Cyrus, Maxx Morando, Shawn Everett, Jonathan Rado, and Michael PollackPerformed by Miley Cyrus', 'https://www.imdb.com/title/tt36590404/soundtrack/?ref_=tt_dyk_snd']}
